channel.title: RSPS Challenge
channel.description:
Well I was challenged today to make a RSPS and have 70 players online by my cousin so thats what im going to do. i will need a vps so help would be appreciated. if you would like to help please pm me. He handed me a usb with a blank winterlove server and a silab client but that wont work anymore so i downloaded the moparscape client. i will not be posting my tuts anymore you can learn by going to the rpgmaker website and click on tutorials. thanks guys.
GML Programmer
